 de 3e cycle de physique ou de chimie de la matière condensée, et aux ingénieurs.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aSurface chemistry. 0aSurfaces (Physics). 4aMaterials. 7aTechnology & Engineering / Materials Science / General.2bisacsh1 aMüller, Pierre, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102411008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015z978311075641840uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-0293-740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759802937423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759802937/original  a978-3-11-075641-8  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015c2001d2015  a978-3-11-102411-0  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2008d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CHCOMSGSEN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK